text: yeung nung bangheanh aoy puokke kheunh nouv phosdo tang robsa yeung nowknong piphoplok nih ning knong khluon robsa puokke phtal rhaut tealte vea cheakchbasa samreab puokke tha pitabrakd nasa vea( kompir kuor- an) kuchea karpit . tae mcheasa robsa anak min krobkrean teryy del trong pitchea anak thveusaeaksaei leu avei teangoasa noh
